  * Added /usr/lib/tcl8.5 to a search path for tclConfig.sh and /usr/lib/tk8.5
    to a search path for tkConfig.sh in tcl.m4.
  * Removed TK_INC_DIR from tkConfig.sh and tcl.m4.
  * Bumped debhelper compatibility to 5.

